values: This is a locked journal that is a part of a roleplaying game. I am in not, I repeat not Kenny Vasoli, nor am I affiliated with him or The Starting Line in any way, shape, or form. Please don't add my journal unless you are a member of the MBP universe - any non-members can, and will, be ban_set. If you are, however, feel free to comment and ask me to be added. Or just add me, whatever floats your boat. Thank you. Furthermore - THIS IS NOT A GRAPHICS JOURNAL. I look through tons of bullshit to find my pictures, so don't assume just because you're stumbling across this journal that means my icons are fair game to you, too. And I reccomend not fullsizing them, either, in whatever have you community; I'm a heinous bitch, and won't hesitate to be so to you. Tyvm. Keep moving along now.
